And I truly believe that he will.

37:38.674 --> 37:40.776
And so I would encourage you, sign up today.

37:40.836 --> 37:42.738
We want to get that book in your hands this week.

37:43.079 --> 37:46.022
I know that there are a number of you who are doing this already.

37:46.082 --> 37:48.124
And I want to thank you for that.

37:48.484 --> 37:52.849
And many of you have said, hey, you know, like Leslie and I, we want to go above this.

37:53.089 --> 37:54.371
How can we even push further?

37:54.431 --> 37:55.672
We want to see God do more.

37:55.872 --> 37:57.414
And I just want to thank you for that.

37:58.115 --> 38:01.919
Those of you who give financially, you're making an incredible difference.

38:02.239 --> 38:02.760
Let me pray.

38:03.440 --> 38:04.882
God, we come to you today.

38:06.786 --> 38:16.196
with a desire to trust you more, to know you present in our lives more, to experience your freedom in our lives more.

38:16.316 --> 38:20.982
And we know that comes through generosity when it comes to our finances.

38:22.623 --> 38:24.225
It comes to knowing that you're enough.

38:25.046 --> 38:26.868
It comes to deciding what's enough.

38:28.009 --> 38:30.492
And then it comes to pursuing you with a generous heart.

38:30.512 --> 38:36.018
And it's there that we find our sweet spot, trusting you in relationship with you.

38:38.242 --> 38:44.592
and so God, we come to you today and pray that you would speak to our hearts.

38:45.673 --> 38:49.299
And we don't wanna take some rooms and make them available and other rooms and not.

38:49.379 --> 38:58.313
We wanna open up all the rooms of our heart to you, including our finances and pray that you would speak and pray that you would inspire.

38:58.333 --> 39:03.180
God, we thank you that when we surrender to you, you show up in our lives.

39:03.821 --> 39:06.866
And God, I'm excited about what you're gonna do out of today.

39:07.234 --> 39:12.903
excited about the way you're going to show up in people's lives, excited about the way that you're going to work.

39:13.724 --> 39:27.966
And God, thank you for the honor and the privilege it is to invest in what you're doing, to be a part of the mission that you have called us to, that we might see lives change, including our own.

39:27.986 --> 39:30.290
And we pray this in your name.

39:30.310 --> 39:30.610
Amen.

